                        >
                        <span class="small" style="color:#c0c0d0;">
                            Operating at atmospheric pressure is what makes the
                            system practical, but it's also what makes
                            maintaining non-equilibrium hardest. They're
                            fighting thermodynamics on both sides of the energy
                            budget.</span
                        >
