                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ==================== SLIDE 13: Summary ==================== -->
            <div class="slide" id="slide-summary">
                <div class="content">
                    <h2>Physics Assessment Summary</h2>
                    <p style="margin-bottom:1.2em;">
                        How realistic is each claim in the UAP proposal?
                    </p>
                    <div
                        style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto auto; gap:0; max-width:820px; margin:0 auto; text-align:left; font-size:clamp(0.85rem,1.3vw,1.05rem);"
                    >
                        <!-- Header -->
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.5em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color:#6b7280; font-weight:600;"
                        >
                            Claim
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.5em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color:#6b7280; font-weight:600; text-align:center;"
                        >
                            Verdict
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.5em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color:#6b7280; font-weight:600;"
                        >
                            Note
                        </div>
                        <!-- Row 1 -->
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#c0c0d0;"
                        >
                            Cold plasma at 200&ndash;300&deg;C via microwaves
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); text-align:center;"
                        >
                            <span style="color:#34d399; font-weight:600;"
                                >Realistic</span>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#6b7280;"
                        >
                            Well established industrially
                        </div>
                        <!-- Row 2 -->
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#c0c0d0;"
                        >
                            Selective ionization by tuning electron energy
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); text-align:center;"
                        >
                            <span style="color:#f59e0b; font-weight:600;"
                                >Plausible</span>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#6b7280;"
                        >
                            O<sub>2</sub>/Xe overlap at ~12 eV
                        </div>
                        <!-- Row 3 -->
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#c0c0d0;"
                        >
                            E&times;B drift separates ions from neutrals
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); text-align:center;"
                        >
                            <span style="color:#34d399; font-weight:600;"
                                >Realistic</span>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#6b7280;"
                        >
                            Fundamental Lorentz force
                        </div>
                        <!-- Row 4 -->
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#c0c0d0;"
                        >
                            Larmor radius sorts ions by mass
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); text-align:center;"
                        >
                            <span style="color:#f59e0b; font-weight:600;"
                                >Hard at 1 bar</span>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color:#6b7280;"
                        >
                            65 nm mean free path
                        </div>
                        <!-- Row 5 -->
                        <div style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; color:#c0c0d0;">
                            Non-equilibrium maintained at atmospheric pressure
                        </div>
                        <div style="padding:0.6em 1em; text-align:center;">
                            <span style="color:#ef4444; font-weight:600;"
                                >Open question</span>
                        </div>
                        <div style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; color:#6b7280;">
                            Thermalization vs. selectivity
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        style="margin-top:1.5em; max-width:820px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"
                    >
                        <p
                            style="font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:0.5em;"
                        >
                            Open Questions
                        </p>
                        <div
                            style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:0.8em; text-align:left;"
                        >
                            <div
                                style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius:8px;"
                            >
                                <p class="small" style="color:#c0c0d0;">
                                    What is the actual collection efficiency at
                                    1 bar? The collision rate suggests
                                    significant yield loss.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius:8px;"
                            >
                                <p class="small" style="color:#c0c0d0;">
                                    How much energy goes to waste heat vs.
                                    useful ionization? This determines whether
                                    the economics work.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius:8px;"
                            >
                                <p class="small" style="color:#c0c0d0;">
                                    Can T<sub>g</sub> be held below 300&deg;C at production-scale
                                    throughput without active cooling?
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                style="padding:0.6em 0.8em; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius:8px;"
                            >
                                <p class="small" style="color:#c0c0d0;">
                                    What purity levels are achievable given the
                                    O<sub>2</sub>/Xe ionization overlap?
